      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped root veg</strong>, <strong>apple wedges</strong>, <strong>crushed garlic </strong>and your <strong>bay leaf[ves] </strong>to a large, deep baking tray (or <strong>oven-proof dish</strong>)</p><p>Tip: Don't overcrowd the tray, use two if you need to!</p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
