      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat it dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper</p><p>Combine your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> with a pinch of <strong>black pepper</strong> in a large bowl</p><p>Add the<strong> salad </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>balsamic salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
