    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Squeeze the <strong>roasted garlic </strong>out of the skins into the bake, discard the skin and give it all a good mix up</p><p>Serve the <strong>sticky sausage, apple & root veg bake</strong> and pour over any <strong>remaining juices </strong>from the tray[s]</p><p>Serve the<strong> balsamic salad</strong> to the side and sprinkle your<strong> pumpkin seeds</strong> all over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
